---
import {
    LogoIcon,
    LocationIcon,
    PhoneIcon,
    MailIcon,
    LinkedInIcon,
} from "./assets/Icons";
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900">
    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-2 py-8 border-b border-gray-700 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 justify-between"
    >
        <div class="md:w-1/3">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 h-8">
                <LogoIcon />
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">WebCraft</span>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
                Transformamos ideas en experiencias digitales excepcionales.
                Diseño web moderno y desarrollo de alta calidad para tu negocio.
            </p>
        </div>

        <nav>
            <ul
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 tracking-wider"
            >
                <li><a href="#services" data-scroll>Servicios</a></li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#why-choose-us" data-scroll>¿Por qué elegirnos?</a>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#our-process" data-scroll>Nuestro proceso</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact-us" data-scroll>Contáctanos</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-5 px-4 md:px-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 justify-between text-gray-400"
    >
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <LocationIcon />
                <p>Bogotá DC, Colombia</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <PhoneIcon />
                <p>+57 301 570 3750</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <MailIcon />
                <p>yonkitas9@gmail.com</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jhonatandavidbecerradonado-frontend/"
                    class="hover:text-primary-400 flex gap-2"
                >
                    <LinkedInIcon />
                    <p>Jhonatan Becerra</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p>
            &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} WebCraft. Todos los derechos reservados.
        </p>
    </div>
</footer>
